  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Produce 30 Films to foster use of Niuean Language</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project will help produce at least 30 short films in Niuean language, Niue language sub-titling will be on all the films, Niuean language sub-titling also on films narrated in other languages, subtitling lyrics in film songs programmes shown on TV Niue in the same Niuean language as audio. This will help over 20,000 Niuean people to learn and use the Niuean Language on a regular basis.  The short films produced will be showcased in the &quot;KIFAGA NIUE FILM FESTIVAL&quot; planned for February 2014.</narrative>
  </description>
